init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You call the number and are greeted by a voice on the other end.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are going to be a member of the Illuminati.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: We decide that the world needs to be reset.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: We decide to put our people in charge of the government.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: We decide to do this by releasing a virus that will make the people sick and eventually turn them into lizards.
